Dependencies: mpv

Installation:

mv db.json.init db.json

ln -s $(readlink -f YTPlayer.py) ~/bin/ytplayer

ln -s $(readlink -f YTVote.py) ~/bin/ytvote

Edit both YTPlayer and YTVote do that dbfile="absolute path to your db.json file"

Usage:

ytplayer &>/dev/null &

ytvote cmd

cmd:

- up

- down

- remove

If you like it send me a message and I will make it more user friendly or add more functions
